- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to improve SSL algorithms, which is a common problem in AI. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The experiments are conducted on image datasets, and the proposed algorithm is evaluated on image classification tasks. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The proposed algorithm could potentially be applied to natural language processing tasks, such as text classification. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The proposed algorithm involves training neural networks and could be considered a type of neural computing.
